---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Bibliografia · IA · Saúde"
description: "Bibliografia consolidada de IA · Saúde · papers, guidelines, regulamentação, ferramentas e Wikipedia."
permalink: /pt-PT/bibliografia/
---

<div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20">
  <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-medium text-blue-600">
    <a href="{% p 'pt-PT/' %}" class="hover:underline">← voltar à aula</a>
  </p>
  <h1 class="mb-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl">Bibliografia</h1>

  <p class="mb-8 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-600">
    Todas as referências citadas na aula, agrupadas por tipo. Cada link abre a fonte original. <strong>{{ bibliografia.entries.length }}</strong> entradas.
  </p>

  <div class="mb-10 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
    <div class="mb-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">BibTeX · copia para o teu gestor de referências</div>
    <textarea id="bib-textarea" readonly class="h-32 w-full resize-none rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white p-3 font-mono text-xs text-slate-700" aria-label="bibtex">{{ bibliografia.bibText }}</textarea>
    <button type="button" id="copy-bib" class="mt-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">copiar BibTeX</button>
  </div>

  {% for key, meta in bibliografia.groups %}
    {% set items = bibliografia.entries | selectattr("type", "equalto", key) | list %}
    {% if items.length > 0 %}
    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="mb-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">
        <span>{{ meta.icon }}</span>{{ meta.label }}<span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500">· {{ items.length }}</span>
      </h2>
      <ol class="space-y-3">
        {% for e in items %}
        <li class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-800">{{ e.cite }}</p>
          <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap items-baseline gap-3 text-xs">
            <a href="{{ e.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-mono text-blue-700 underline underline-offset-2 hover:no-underline">{{ e.url }}</a>
            <span class="text-slate-500">· em {{ e.section }}</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ol>
    </section>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}

  <p class="mt-12 rounded-lg border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 p-4 text-sm text-amber-900">
    Encontraste uma afirmação na aula sem fonte? Abre uma <a href="https://github.com/tiagojct/ia-na-saude/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:no-underline">issue no GitHub</a>.
  </p>
</div>

<script>
  (function () {
    const btn = document.getElementById("copy-bib");
    btn?.addEventListener("click", async function () {
      const ta = document.getElementById("bib-textarea");
      if (!ta) return;
      try {
        await navigator.clipboard.writeText(ta.value);
        const original = btn.textContent;
        btn.textContent = "copiado ✓";
        btn.classList.add("bg-green-600");
        setTimeout(function () {
          btn.textContent = original;
          btn.classList.remove("bg-green-600");
        }, 1800);
      } catch (e) {
        ta.select();
        document.execCommand("copy");
      }
    });
  })();
</script>
